53. Write a Python program to calculate surface volume  and area of a cylinder.

import math
radius = float (input ("Enter the radius of the cylinder: "))
height = float (input ("Enter the height of the cylinder: "))
surface_area = 2 * math.pi * radius * (height + radius)
volume = math.pi * radius * radius * height
print ("Surface Area of the cylinder is:", surface_area)
print ("Volume of the cylinder is:", volume)
print ("The area of the triangle is:", area)
